snippet.title: Astro Hunters VR - Official Release Window Announcement Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Astro Hunters VR is a VR multiplayer extraction shooter developed by Wenkly Studio. Players will gather resources across the galaxy to upgrade and establish an arsenal to take on powerful enemies. Team up with other players to complete missions and gain rewards for successfully extracting loot. Astro Hunters VR is launching on SteamVR and Meta Quest in Q3 2024.
